visual_content: Logo for 'chargers'. Text: 'Get 10% Discount On Your Order Copy the code and shop at evchargers.com.au'. A dashed box containing the code 'BF10' and a button that says 'Tap To Copy'.

A promotional banner displaying '10% OFF EV CHARGING SAVE ON EV CHARGING'. It features a green electric car graphic and stylized lightning bolts. Below this, there are input fields for 'Mobile/UPI ID' and 'Charge Amount (Points)', and a 'Start Charging' button.

A promotional image with "ChargeHub SAVE 20% OFF YOUR FIRST CHARGE" text, an image of a silver electric car, and a code "EVSTART20" with a "COPY CODE" button. A barcode is visible. Text indicates 'Valid for new users only. Limited time offer.'
An image depicting a silver electric car charging at a station. Text reads 'SAVE 20% OFF YOUR FIRST CHARGE' and 'EVSTART20 COPY CODE'. Below the code is a URL 'chargehub.com/promos' and a QR code.
Large text displaying "10% OFF DISCOUNT ON CHARGING" with a graphic of an electric plug within a green box.

A bright, colorful coupon-like image with the text 'ZAP! 20% OFF EV CHARGE! SUPERCHARGE YOUr RIDE!'. It features an illustration of a blue electric car and a charging station. There is also a barcode visible at the bottom of the coupon.
